Sorry to say but if you wanted to add the kills to the db all you need to change is

CREATE TABLE `rscd_kills` ( `user` bigint(20) NOT NULL default '0', `killed` bigint(20) NOT NULL default '0', `time` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL default '0', `type` tinyint(1) unsigned NOT NULL default '1', PRIMARY KEY (`user`,`killed`,`time`) ) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

Not needed.
[/quote]So let me guess yours have got the incorrect table for the SQL for rscd_Kills that is why it isnt importing the user Kills into the db? all you need to do it add the correct one what i have put above and bang it will work correctly
